### Frontend

| التقنية | الإصدار | الاستخدام |
|---------|---------|-----------|
| React | 18.3 | UI Framework |
| TypeScript | 5.6 | Type Safety |
| Vite | 7.3 | Build Tool + Dev Server |
| Tailwind CSS | 3.4 | Styling (مع Tailwind Animate) |
| shadcn/ui (Radix) | latest | 47 مكون UI جاهز |
| TanStack React Query | 5.60 | State Management + API Cache |
| Wouter | 3.3 | Client Routing (SPA) |
| React Hook Form + Zod | latest | Form Validation |
| Framer Motion | 11.13 | Animations |
| Recharts | 2.15 | Charts & Analytics |
| Lucide Icons | 0.453 | Icon Library |

### Backend

| التقنية | الإصدار | الاستخدام |
|---------|---------|-----------|
| Express.js | 4.21 | HTTP Server |
| TypeScript | 5.6 | Type Safety |
| PostgreSQL | 15 | Database |
| Drizzle ORM | 0.39 | ORM + Migrations |
| WebSocket (ws) | 8.19 | Real-time Communication |
| JWT (jsonwebtoken) | 9.0 | Authentication (User + Admin tokens) |
| bcryptjs | 3.0 | Password Hashing |
| chess.js | 1.4 | Chess Game Engine |
| express-rate-limit | 8.2 | Rate Limiting |
| Node.js | 20.x | Runtime |

### Infrastructure

| التقنية | الاستخدام |
|---------|-----------|
| Docker + Docker Compose | Containerization |
| Nginx | Reverse Proxy + SSL + Load Balancing |
| PM2 | Process Manager (Cluster Mode) |
| Capacitor | Mobile App (Android/iOS) |
| Flutter WebView | Alternative Mobile Wrapper |
| Service Worker | PWA + Push Notifications |
| Let's Encrypt / Certbot | Free SSL |

