## 🐳 Docker & Deployment

### Docker Compose Services

```yaml
db:        PostgreSQL 15 Alpine — Health check, persistent volume
app:       Node 20 Alpine — Multi-stage build, depends on DB health
nginx:     Nginx Alpine — Reverse proxy (optional profile)
```

### Dockerfile (Multi-stage)

- **Stage 1 (Builder)**: Install all deps → Build client (Vite) + server (esbuild → dist/index.cjs)
- **Stage 2 (Production)**: Production deps only + drizzle-kit for migrations

### PM2 Production Config

- Cluster mode (all CPU cores)
- 1GB max memory restart
- JSON logs in `/var/log/vex/`
- Graceful shutdown (10s kill timeout)
- Deploy hooks for auto `npm ci → build → reload`

### Nginx Config (Production — 20k+ users)

- Rate limiting zones (API 30r/s, Auth 10r/m, Strict 5r/m)
- TLS 1.2/1.3, HSTS with preload
- WebSocket `/ws` with 24h timeout
- Static assets: 1-year cache immutable
- Security: blocked .git/.env, wp-admin attack paths

---

## 📱 Mobile App

### Capacitor (Primary)

- App ID: `click.vixo.app`
- Splash: Dark background #0f1419
- Plugins: SplashScreen, StatusBar, Keyboard, PushNotifications
- Build: `npm run build → npx cap sync → Android Studio/Xcode`

### Flutter WebView (Alternative)

- WebView + Connectivity monitoring
- Arabic UI for error states
- External URL detection → system browser
- Back button = WebView history then exit dialog

### PWA (Web)

- Service Worker: Cache-first (static), Network-first (API)
- Push Notifications with actions
- Installable (manifest.json with icons 64→512px)
- Offline support

