## 🔧 الأوامر المهمة (KEY COMMANDS)

```bash
# Development
npm run dev                    # Start dev server (port 3001)
npm run check                  # TypeScript type check
npm run db:push                # Push schema to DB

# Production Build
npm run build                  # Build client (Vite) + server (esbuild)
npm start                      # Start production server

# Docker
docker-compose up -d           # Start all services
docker-compose --profile with-nginx up -d   # With Nginx
docker-compose exec app npx drizzle-kit push # Run migrations
docker-compose exec app npx tsx scripts/seed-data.ts # Seed data

# Database
npx drizzle-kit push           # Push schema changes
npx tsx scripts/seed-data.ts   # Seed currencies + payment methods + games
```

---

## 🔑 Environment Variables

### Required

```
DATABASE_URL          — PostgreSQL connection string
SESSION_SECRET        — Min 32 chars
JWT_SIGNING_KEY       — User JWT secret
ADMIN_JWT_SECRET      — Admin JWT secret (مختلف عن User)
```

### Optional Integrations

```
SENDGRID_API_KEY      — Email notifications
TWILIO_*              — SMS/OTP
GOOGLE_CLIENT_*       — Google OAuth
FACEBOOK_APP_*        — Facebook OAuth
TELEGRAM_BOT_TOKEN    — Telegram auth
STRIPE_*              — Payment gateway
FIREBASE_*            — Push notifications
```

